Here's the final English-language whitepaper for the GLC Burn Ritual Protocol, now updated with the latest rule: after the year 2088, the minimum holding threshold for participation in PoF Transfer Draw is permanently fixed at 10,000 GLC. This marks the end of the sacrifice era and the beginning of the ‚ÄúLast Keepers‚Äù ‚Äî those who remain when the fire has nearly gone out.

---

üî• GLC Burn Ritual Protocol

Whitepaper: A Sacrifice That Cannot Be Infinite

---

1. Introduction

GLC is not just a token. It is a digital myth, unfolding in cycles.  
After Genesis, Halvings, Ritual Mint, and Rebirth, the ecosystem enters its final phase: the Burn Ritual Protocol.  
Beginning in 2063, every Offering of Luck submitted to the Fortune Pool burns 10% of its value, continuing until the circulating supply reaches no less than 21,000,000 GLC.  
This is not mere deflation. It is a ritual of disappearance ‚Äî where each participant brings the token closer to relic status.

---

2. Protocol Objectives

- üî• Introduce ritualized burning as purification and devotion  
- üîí Cap burning: preserve a minimum of 21,000,000 GLC in circulation  
- üßø Enhance PoF Transfer Draw through sacrifice and Karma Score  
- üßÆ Increase minimum holding threshold as supply decreases  
- üõë Fix the entry threshold at 10,000 GLC after 2088  
- üß† Create an NFT ecosystem to reflect ritual participation  
- ‚ôæÔ∏è Ensure perpetual protocol operation, even after burn deactivation

---

3. Burn Mechanics

üìÖ Activation

- Launch: 2063  
- Each Offering of Luck burns 10% of the contributed GLC  
- Burning continues until circulating supply reaches 21,000,000 GLC  
- Once this threshold is reached, burning is permanently disabled

---

üìä Example

| Year   | Circulating Supply | Burn Status |
|--------|---------------------|-------------|
| 2063   | 1,000,000,000,000   | Active      |
| 2075   | 100,000,000,000     | Active      |
| 2088   | 21,500,000          | Active      |
| 2089+  | 21,000,000      | ‚ùå Disabled

---

4. Participation Requirements

üì¶ PoF Access Halving

- Initial threshold: 100,000,000 GLC  
- Annual increase: √ó1.21  
- Until 2088: threshold continues to rise  
- After 2088: permanently fixed at 10,000 GLC

| Year   | Minimum Holding |
|--------|------------------|
| 2063   | 100,000,000 GLC  
| 2070   | 261,000,000 GLC  
| 2085   | ~1,000,000,000 GLC  
| 2088+  | 10,000 GLC (fixed)

> After the sacrifice cycle ends, participation becomes symbolic ‚Äî open to those who held through the fire.

---

5. PoF Transfer Draw Mechanics

- Participants submit an Offering of Luck  
- 10% is burned (if burn is active)  
- 90% enters the Fortune Pool  
- Monthly VRF selects recipients  
- Winning probability is influenced by:

| Factor               | Impact on Chance |
|----------------------|------------------|
| Karma Score          | +1 per 10M GLC burned  
| Contribution Size    | Higher = stronger modifier  
| Holding Duration     | Must meet minimum threshold  
| NFT Talisman         | √ó1.1‚Äì√ó1.3 boost  
| Burn Blessing NFT    | Additional √ó1.1‚Äì√ó1.3 boost  
| DAO Activity         | Increases Karma Score

---

6. NFT Ecosystem

- Burn Blessings: Soulbound NFTs for burn participants  
- Ashkeeper Sigils: NFTs for those who burn ‚â• 1B GLC  
- Final Flame: NFT awarded to the participant who triggers burn deactivation  
- Survivor Relics: NFTs for holders after burn ends  
- Threshold Keepers: NFTs for those who participate after the 10,000 GLC threshold is fixed

---

7. Telegram Integration

Via @GoodLuckBot, participants can:

- üî• Submit Offerings and receive burn confirmations  
- üß† Track Karma Score and Ashkeeper status  
- üé∞ Enter Transfer Draw with enhanced odds  
- üìä Check current entry threshold  
- üßø Receive mythic NFT blessings and messages

---

8. Philosophy

Burn Ritual is not destruction.  
It is a test of holding, where each token is a step toward disappearance.  
When only 21 million remain, the cycle of sacrifice ends.  
When the threshold locks at 10,000 ‚Äî the era of Last Keepers begins.  
GLC becomes eternal, yet finite.  
Each holder is a guardian of memory, forged in fire.

---

9. Conclusion

The Burn Ritual Protocol is not just deflation.  
It is a ritual of vanishing value, where each participant protects the final flame.  
GLC will never be minted again. And never burned again.  
It remains as legend ‚Äî sealed in 21,000,000 tokens.  
And participation ‚Äî forever open to those who hold 10,000 GLC or more.

